+### ImpureStaticProperty
+
+Emitted when attempting to use a static property from a function or method marked as pure
+
+```php
+class ValueHolder {
+    public static ?string $value = null;
+
+    /**
+     * @psalm-pure
+     */
+    public static function get(): ?string {
+        return self::$value;
+    }
+}
+```
